videos.headline: Tennessee returns blocked punt for TD
videos.description: Tennessee's Romello Edwards blocks Chattanooga's punt and Brandon John returns it 24 yards for a Volunteers' TD.

videos.headline: Tennessee's Guarantano finds Jennings wide-open for TD
videos.description: Tennessee QB Jarrett Guarantano tosses a 12-yard pass to WR Jauan Jennings, who makes a wide-open catch in the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tennessee's Guarantano finds Jennings wide-open for TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tennessee's Guarantano connects with Callaway for TD
videos.description: Tennessee QB Jarrett Guarantano lobs a 38-yard pass into the end zone and WR Marquez Callaway makes the grab for a touchdown.
